page.title: 20WHO DID THE WORK
page.content:
All the information was suggested and collected, and typed in by the 26 pupils in Class 1 of Tedburn St Mary County Primary School.
We are all 10 or 11 years old.
Only 15 of us actually live in the area designated, the remainder come from Whitestone, etc. {Our names are: Myles Underhill, Katrina Milverton, Philip Skuse, Stephen Carter, Andrea Risdon, Thomas Berman, Tina Shilston, Mark Sibley, Adam Brewer, Selwyn Anthony, Alan Sabine, Daniel Hawkins, Nicholas Woolacott, Helen Strong, Heather Craythorn, Karen Spooner, Matthew Wood, Beth Earle, John Bastin, Mark Roberts, Amanda Hambly, Amanda Bridewell, Nathan Littlewood, Esther Ley, Peter Northcott, David Williams.
